shape: sequence_diagram

Projectile: Projectile
CollisionSystem: Collision System
Enemy: Enemy
HealthSystem: Health System

Projectile -> CollisionSystem: update position
CollisionSystem -> CollisionSystem: check bounds overlap
CollisionSystem -> CollisionSystem: perform collision test
CollisionSystem -> Enemy: notify collision
CollisionSystem -> Projectile: mark for removal
Enemy -> HealthSystem: take damage event
HealthSystem -> Enemy: apply damage
HealthSystem -> Enemy: check health <= 0
Enemy -> Enemy: trigger death state
Enemy -> CollisionSystem: remove from collision grid

